title: Viral Video Claiming Officer Helped ‘Rig’ Pak Elections is False
subtitle: A viral video showing a female Pakistani polling officer claims that she allowed ‘cheating’ over the course of voting during the recently concluded national election at her booth.
author: www.thequint.com
vclaim:
A viral video showing a female Pakistani polling officer claims that she allowed ‘cheating’ over the course of voting during the recently concluded national election at her booth.

At the time of writing this, the video had over 6,700 shares.
